{"text_id":158586,"tokens":["Our"," work"," investigates"," the"," dramatic"," variability"," of"," X","-","ray"," absorption"," lines"," in"," the"," acc","ret","ing"," binary"," system"," Cy","gnus"," X","-","1","."," Observations"," from"," the"," Chandra"," X","-","ray"," Observatory"," reveal"," profound"," changes"," in"," the"," equivalent"," widths"," and"," fluxes"," of"," absorption"," lines"," across"," different"," orbital"," phases","."," This"," variability"," challenges"," the"," traditional"," view"," of"," steady"," accretion"," and"," highlights"," the"," dynamic"," nature"," of"," matter"," inflow"," onto"," the"," black"," hole","."," We"," propose"," that"," the"," observed"," absorption"," variations"," are"," likely"," caused"," by"," intricate"," interplay"," between"," changes"," in"," the"," density"," and"," ionization"," state"," of"," the"," intervening"," plasma"," along"," the"," line"," of"," sight","."," Our"," findings"," suggest"," that"," the"," accretion"," disk"," in"," Cy","gnus"," X","-","1"," undergoes"," significant"," geometric"," and"," physical"," changes"," during"," its"," orbital"," period","."," Additionally",","," we"," observed"," narrow"," absorption"," lines",","," attributed"," to"," highly"," ionized"," iron",","," which"," provides"," strong"," constraints"," on"," the"," magnetic"," field"," strength"," near"," the"," black"," hole","."," These"," results"," demonstrate"," the"," crucial"," role"," of"," absorption"," lines"," in"," unravel","ing"," the"," complex"," accretion"," processes"," and"," the"," physical"," conditions"," in"," the"," vicinity"," of"," acc","ret","ing"," black"," holes","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}